description.narrative: 1. Suspected Hazardous Areas and Hazardous Areas assigned by LibMAC are released in accordance with National Standards to the benefit of the affected community. 2. Awareness of landmines, ERW and IED related risks for women, men, and children in contaminated areas is increased through Risk Education.
DCA will deliver a 12-month intervention to contribute to human security in and around the city of Derna in Libya
